HEADWORD: Trinucleus
<hw>Tri*nu"cle*us</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>tri-</ets> + <ets>nucleus</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Paleon.)</fld> <def>A
